1 & planned & planned & planned & planned & planned & planned &
Predicted to equal the \(K = 10\) baseline on every fixture (single-pass
convergence). \\
2 & planned & planned & planned & planned & planned & planned & Expected
identical to \(K = 1\) (no second-pass additions on any shipped
fixture). \\
